10 yena patrāṇi, kampamānāni, śīghram 11 sarvāṇi eva anataḥ atha vā namrāṇi abhavan 12 yatra prathamam chāyāṃ kṣiptaḥ āsīt puṇyaḥ parvataḥ;
13 tathāpi taiḥ sva-sthānāt na vibhaktāni 14 yāvat, yathā pakṣiṇaḥ vṛkṣa-śikhara-sthitāḥ 15 viramereyuḥ sarvakarmāṇi sva-śilpāni;
