19 yathā śākhāyāḥ śākhāyām saṃgṛhṇāti 20 pinākāvanyasmim Chiassi-tīre, 21 yadā vāyuḥ dakṣiṇa-pūrva-diśāyāḥ muktaḥ bhavati.

